{
  "stem": "5639.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with great pride, and in great humility, I am telling you that a few weeks ago, I got a notification from the [NON-ENGLISH] from Israel that he was honored as one of the Righteous Among Nations.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Upon my instigation.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was the German, Alfred Rossner upon my instigation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it's a whole long story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are jumping ahead a little bit, but not very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's a-- he was a very unusual figure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was-- he was fighting the system, and paid for it with his own life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was hanged by the Gestapo for helping and abetting Jews in January 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Definitely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He prolonged the life of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In any day-- he made it productive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He offered the Germans a production of winter uniforms to be sent to the Russian front, which was enormous.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the height of-- of the ghetto, he employed 6,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, and each worker, thanks to him, was allowed to protect two members of his family-- either his or her parents, or a spouse and a child.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in fact, there were 18,000 Jews untouched.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was in constant disagreement and in constant friction with the Judenrat, who sadly had to produce Jews for deportatiom And here there was a ghetto who had about 27,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The actual ghetto, in the sense that we understand ghetto, was in Bedzin established very late.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was established at the beginning of 1943, just prior to the ethnic cleansing-- how I hate that expression-- just prior to the-- the Final Solution-- to the implementation of Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We lived so far in the restricted areas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did not need guards because it was-- I mean, we were normal people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew what it means to obey law.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
